title: Mini Shushi Xiaochi - Mini Vegetarian Snack
description: Several vegan options if you clearly specify. The location is near to the statue of the Yellow River Mother. Take Bus 31, 76, 102, 106 or 141 and get off at Little West Lake station (小西湖站). Chinese name: 迷你蔬食小. Address in Chinese: 七里河区小西湖东街128号.
streetAddress: 128 Little West Lake, East Street: Qilihe District
